name: Winry Inu
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
$WINRY is a decentralised project on the Ethereum network (ERC-20). 

Winry Inu is a New Born Cryptocurrency based on Anime Character named Winry. A Community-driven project with leading professional Developers and Marketing Gurus. At Winry, we work together as a community to become the next biggest anime project in the Metaverse!

We are committed to build the number 1
Decentralised Ecosystem and Metaverse Anime World from which the entire Anime lovers can express truly themselves.
Our goal is to support and contribute to a safe place to trade your valuable cryptocurrency.
